OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Sejal Karia
OL,7,Fexplores why the police's use of
OL,8,Ffacial recognition technology is
OL,9,Fproving controversial
OL,11,FWords by ITV News Correspondent Sejal
OL,12,FKaria and Investigations Producer
OL,13,FKieran Carter
OL,15,FIt's been described as the greatest
OL,16,Finnovation in policing since
OL,17,Ffingerprinting. Live facial
OL,18,Frecognition (LFR) technology is
OL,19,Fincreasingly being used by police
OL,20,Fforces across the country in the fight
OL,21,Fagainst crime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
