OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FThis year alone, London's Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice says it's helped officers
OL,8,Farrest 540 individuals wanted for
OL,9,Fcriminal behaviour.
OL,11,FOf these arrests, more than 50 were of
OL,12,Findividuals allegedly involved in
OL,13,Fviolence against women and girls,
OL,14,Fincluding strangulation, stalking,
OL,15,Fdomestic abuse and rape.
OL,17,FIn addition, the Met has arrested over
OL,18,F50 sex offenders who were found to be
OL,19,Fin breach of their court conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
