OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FSigns are placed nearby to tell the
OL,7,Fpublic their faces are being scanned.
OL,8,FIf they don't match a photo on file
OL,9,Ftheir image is automatically deleted.
OL,11,FInside the van, officers monitor
OL,12,Fscreens which alert them if the
OL,13,Fcameras spot a match.
OL,15,FWe didn't have to wait long.
OL,17,FWithin minutes, someone triggered an
OL,18,Falert. Their face had been caught by
OL,19,Fthe cameras on top of the van and
OL,20,Fchecked against over 15,000 people on
OL,21,Fthe police "watchlist" that day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
