OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FAll individuals wanted for alleged
OL,7,Fcriminal offences or with court
OL,8,Fconditions imposed upon them.
OL,10,FThis man, a registered sex offender. A
OL,11,Ffew checks reveal he's adhering to the
OL,12,Fconditions imposed on him - and they
OL,13,Flet him go.
OL,15,FTo see how quickly the technology
OL,16,Fcould work, we put my photo onto the
OL,17,Fday's watchlist. In less than a second
OL,18,Fof walking into the camera's range, an
OL,19,Falarm went off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
