OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FNearby officers received a side-by-
OL,7,Fside comparison of my face and what
OL,8,Fthe cameras have seen on a handheld
OL,9,Fdevice. It's then up to them to decide
OL,10,Fif I am who the computer says.
OL,12,FBy the end of the day there'd been
OL,13,Fnine alerts in total, all of them
OL,14,Fcorrectly identifying someone on the
OL,15,Fpolice's watchlist. Six were of sexual
OL,16,Foffenders who were found to be
OL,17,Fcomplying with the conditions of their
OL,18,Frelease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
