OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FThe other three led to arrests, one of
OL,7,Fwhich involved a man wanted for six
OL,8,Fdifferent offences of theft.
OL,10,FThe Met Police says its LFR cameras
OL,11,Fhave scanned over 700,00 faces this
OL,12,Fyear. Over 1000 triggered alerts, but
OL,13,F27 of these were recorded as "false" `
OL,14,Fessentially the computer getting it
OL,15,Fwrong.
OL,17,FOne of those 27 is Shaun Thompson, an
OL,18,Fanti-knife campaigner from London. In
OL,19,FFebruary this year he says he was
OL,20,Fstopped by police during an LFR
OL,21,Fdeployment in London Bridge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
