OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FPolice questioned him about his
OL,7,Fidentity for over 20 minutes, asking
OL,8,Ffor photo ID and fingerprints. He was
OL,9,Feventually let go ` an alleged case of
OL,10,Fmistaken identity he says left him
OL,11,Fshaken.
OL,13,F"It's stop and search on steroids."
OL,14,FShaun Thompson told ITV News.
OL,16,F"That's what I look at that as. It's
OL,17,Fworse than a stop and search. You
OL,18,Fknow, at least you have to be
OL,19,Fsuspected of doing something with a
OL,20,Fstop and search."
