OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FThe police say the locations of their
OL,7,Fdeployments are intelligence led and
OL,8,Ftarget crime hotspots. Shaun told us
OL,9,Fhe felt these areas disproportionately
OL,10,Faffect ethnic communities.
OL,12,FOne of the ways the police combat
OL,13,Fracial bias in this technology is by
OL,14,Fcontrolling how confident the system
OL,15,Fneeds to be it's the wanted individual
OL,16,Fbefore triggering a match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
