OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FA report by the National Physical
OL,7,FLaboratory into LFR says at the levels
OL,8,Fthe police operate there's no risk of
OL,9,Fracial bias, something that's been
OL,10,Fshown to be an issue at lower levels.
OL,11,FDespite this, Shaun's not convinced.
OL,13,F"It's lazy policing," he said.
OL,15,F"You're relying on the machine to scan
OL,16,Fand do your job for you."
