OL,6,FMr Thompson is now bringing a legal
OL,7,Fclaim against the Met Police following
OL,8,Fhis stop in February. The force has
OL,9,Fdeclined to comment on his specific
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,FHuman rights group Big Brother Watch
OL,13,Fis assisting him in this claim.
OL,15,FIts director, Silkie Carlo, was there
OL,16,Fthe night Shaun was stopped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
