OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,F"(It's) potentially the end of privacy
OL,7,Fin this country as we know it. It
OL,8,Fmeans that each of us can be
OL,9,Fbiometrically scanned and checked
OL,10,Fagainst vast databases by the police
OL,11,Ffor absolutely no reason," Ms Carlo
OL,12,Ftold ITV News.
OL,14,F"I think all of us as members of the
OL,15,Fpublic want the police to catch
OL,16,Fcriminals, but we also don't want to
OL,17,Flive in an open prison."
