OL,3,CThe AI technology changing the way
OL,4,Cpolice fight crime
OL,6,FCritics like Big Brother Watch argue
OL,7,Ftechnology like this treats innocent
OL,8,Fmembers of the public as guilty
OL,9,Fsuspects, subjecting them to a
OL,10,Fconstant digital police line-up.
OL,12,F"It completely turns the presumption
OL,13,Fof innocence in this country onto its
OL,14,Fhead.
OL,16,F"Suddenly everyone is a suspect and
OL,17,Fyou have to be cleared by a computer
OL,18,Fsystem, if it gets it wrong, you still
OL,19,Fhave to prove who you are." Ms Carlo
OL,20,Fsaid.
