OL,6,FLindsey Chiswick, the Met Police's
OL,7,Fdirector of intelligence and national
OL,8,Flead on facial recognition disagrees.
OL,10,F"We have a technology here and now
OL,11,Ftoday that has already taken 500
OL,12,Fwanted defenders off the streets of
OL,13,FLondon. As a woman in London, I feel
OL,14,Fsafer knowing that rapists are no
OL,15,Flonger wandering the streets," Ms
OL,16,FChiswick said.
