OL,6,F"I think it's really important to
OL,7,Funderline that an engagement
OL,8,Fconversation doesn't always end in an
OL,9,Farrest. This is normal everyday
OL,10,Fpolicing."
OL,12,FDespite this, Ms Chiswick recognised
OL,13,Fthe need to engage with concerned
OL,14,Fcommunities more.
OL,16,F"I think we need to build trust. And
OL,17,Fthat's what all of the engagement we
OL,18,Fdo is.
