OL,6,F"The Metropolitan Police having done
OL,7,Freally diligent work with an
OL,8,Findependent body so that we understand
OL,9,Fhow we can operate this new technology
OL,10,Fsafely," she added.
OL,12,FTechnology like this has been used by
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police for years. It says
OL,14,Fthat since 2019, it has had no
OL,15,Fmisidentifications and has scanned
OL,16,Fover 2.6 million faces across 72
